==Dutch==

===Proper noun===
'''Miep'''

# A female [[given name]]. Short form the name [[Maria]], the [[Dutch]] equivalent of [[Mary]].

[[Category:Female given names]]

===Dutch female [[hypokoristic]] forming===

In Dutch a typical [[hypokoristic]] pet form forming is to trunk the whole name and add a '''P''' or a '''S''' to it. [[Miep]] and [[Mies]] are such examples.

The Dutch diminutive's form is '''je'''. After a word ending on '''M''' there will be a '''P''' inserted. And after vocals a '''T''' is inserted. 

